{"tid":2081104,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國多個州分疫情反彈 三藩市推遲解除社交限制措施","createTime":"2020-06-27T03:09:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T03:18:40.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"33204c0c60eaa75aead32de47b93ad23782a035c","tid":2081104,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:09:10.000Z","msg":"美國多個州分疫情反彈 三藩市推遲解除社交限制措施<br />\n2020-06-27 HKT 08:19<br />\n<br />\n美國的新型肺炎確診個案超過245萬宗， 12萬4千多人死亡，有超過一半州份，確診個案上升，多個最早重啟經濟活動的南部州分，以及人口眾多的西岸地區，新型肺炎疫情正在反彈。<br />\n<br />\n美國國家過敏症和傳染病研究所所長福奇表示，美國的疫情正面臨嚴重問題，需要大量增加測試，以了解感染疫情的真實數字。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534377-20200627.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534377-20200627.htm&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=4d1bb355\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534377-20200627.htm&h=62f96e55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534377-20200627.htm</a>"},{"pid":"234c02f567994674b7a6b7a14f841410f87a29c6","tid":2081104,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:18:40.000Z","msg":"唔打問題只會越嚟越多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢邊罰關稅<br />\n個邊買返醫療用品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}